{
  "name": "RPlog_Bazil_Revisited",
  "title": "A Word by the Fountain on Caspar",
  "summary": "In Fountain Square at the heart of Plaxton City on Caspar, the mechanic Orson and the Jedi Jessalyn stroll arm in arm while the cloaked bounty hunter Hinrich passes through on his way to the bar. The restless agent Bazil McKenzie approaches the couple and quietly asks Orson to pass word to the smuggler Karrde that he wishes to speak with him, assuring them he means no harm. Their conversation turns to the dangers Orson faces as a hunted man and a new Force student, and Jessalyn presses him not to travel alone; Orson agrees she should come with him. As Bazil drifts off to brood by the fountain and the Caspian officer Tarrin wanders past with his droid, Orson and Jessalyn share quiet Force-sent reassurances and resolve to watch each other's backs.",
